about.description: A program for multi-format in vivo MR spectroscopy conversion to NIFTI.
about.summary: Multi-format in vivo MR spectroscopy conversion to NIfTI

name: spec2nii
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "spec2nii" %}
{% set version = "0.2.7" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2bcf36adfe8ccc40f565ebceaa179b157f0faeb1953308763f7fd3ebdda45959

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"
  entry_points: 
    - spec2nii = spec2nii.spec2nii:main

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.7
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.7
    - numpy
    - nibabel
    - pydicom
    - pymapvbvd
    - scipy

test:
  imports:
    - spec2nii
  commands:
    - spec2nii --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/wexeee/spec2nii
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Multi-format in vivo MR spectroscopy conversion to NIfTI'
  description: |
    A program for multi-format in vivo MR spectroscopy conversion to NIFTI.
  doc_url: https://github.com/wexeee/spec2nii
  dev_url: https://github.com/wexeee/spec2nii

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - wexeee
